OL,3,CClimate scientist sheds light on
OL,4,Cextreme weather as report released
OL,6,FMr Kendon says that the Channel
OL,7,FIslands' geography, combined with
OL,8,Fclimate change, makes them
OL,9,Fincreasingly susceptible to extreme
OL,10,Fweather events in the future.
OL,12,FHe adds: "The Channel Islands are very
OL,13,Fclose to continental Europe, to
OL,14,FFrance, so things like severe
OL,15,Fheatwaves experienced in the near
OL,16,Fcontinent might have quite a
OL,17,Fsignificant influence somewhere like
OL,18,Fthe Channel Islands too."
