OL,3,CClimate scientist sheds light on
OL,4,Cextreme weather as report released
OL,6,FResearchers looking at long-term
OL,7,Fweather records in the UK have found
OL,8,Fno evidence that the islands are
OL,9,Fexperiencing a greater number of
OL,10,Fstorms as a result of climate change.
OL,12,FHowever, studies do show that as the
OL,13,Fclimate continues to warm, the
OL,14,FBailiwicks are likely to experience
OL,15,Fmore rainfall when storms do happen.
OL,17,FStorm Ciaran brought hailstones the
OL,18,Fsize of ice lollies and a tornado to
OL,19,Fthe Channel Islands in November 2023,
OL,20,Fleaving residents displaced and some
OL,21,Fhomes badly damaged.
