OL,3,CClimate scientist sheds light on
OL,4,Cextreme weather as report released
OL,6,FWeather in the Channel Islands
OL,7,Ffollowed similar trends to the UK in
OL,8,F2023.
OL,10,FThe Bailiwicks had their hottest
OL,11,FSeptember ever, while the Howard Davis
OL,12,FWeather Station reported 2023 as
OL,13,FJersey's wettest ever year.
OL,15,FMeanwhile, June 2024 marked the 30th
OL,16,Fmonth in a row where the sea
OL,17,Ftemperature in the Channel Islands had
OL,18,Fbeen above the long-term average.
