OL,3,CClimate scientist sheds light on
OL,4,Cextreme weather as report released
OL,6,FOne marine researcher thinks this
OL,7,Ftemperature increase could be behind
OL,8,Fsome of the wildlife changes he has
OL,9,Fnoticed.
OL,11,FChris Isaacs, a marine expert from the
OL,12,FSociete Jersiaise, explains: "We've
OL,13,Fseen an expansion in the range of
OL,14,Fsouthern species, like some sea slugs,
OL,15,Fwhich never used to be present in the
OL,16,Fisland and we're now finding them in
OL,17,Fquite high numbers.
