OL,3,CClimate scientist sheds light on
OL,4,Cextreme weather as report released
OL,6,F"The Montagu's crab is a local species
OL,7,Fthat used to be quite rare in our
OL,8,Fwaters. We've been carrying out
OL,9,Fintertidal surveys at Portelet in the
OL,10,FNo Take Zone and that's proven the
OL,11,Fspecies is now taking over and
OL,12,Fbehaving invasively as a result of
OL,13,Fwarming sea temperatures."
